title: The Last Guest
occurrences: News Reporter: It is believed there is only one last guest in ROBLOX.
General: What a pleasure it is to meet you, the last guest.
Builderman: Thanks to the last guest's heroic actions. Their leader is dead and his army is fractured from disarray.
Matt: And he was a guest. The last guest.
Colonel: This is Guest1337, known as the "last guest" in ROBLOX.
General: Go with the second family. We already tried capturing the last guest but he eluded us at the orphanage when the police arrived.
General: There is now one last guest remaining in ROBLOX.
General: The last guest....Nobody shoot him! He's mine!
General: What a pleasure it is to meet you, the last guest. Any last words before I blow your brains out?
Soldier: There was an explosion, sir. The last guest has gone and blown up most of the army.
Bacon Soldier: There was an explosion, sir. The last guest has killed the General.
Colonel: Find me the last guest and Jez.
